ARANAUT (VOICEOVER): Princess.

00:09:39.579 --> 00:09:40.613
HAWKTOR (VOICEOVER): You OK, Shun?

00:09:40.713 --> 00:09:41.981
I'm fine.

00:09:42.081 --> 00:09:43.416
COREDEM (VOICE OVER): It's so bright!

00:09:43.516 --> 00:09:45.284
Yeah, really bright.

00:09:45.384 --> 00:09:46.719
AKWIMOS (VOICEOVER): Somethings happening I

00:09:46.819 --> 00:09:48.254
can feel my spirit coming back.

00:09:51.390 --> 00:09:54.493
So is the battle over?

00:09:54.593 --> 00:10:05.604
LINEHALT (VOICEOVER): [roars]

00:10:05.705 --> 00:10:06.572
Drago!

00:10:06.672 --> 00:10:09.909
Drago, come on, buddy.

