Nice and easy.

00:11:56.348 --> 00:11:57.616
Wonderful.

00:11:57.716 --> 00:12:01.053
Why don't you take them both out with your next shot, Dharak?

00:12:01.153 --> 00:12:02.988
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): I could do this all day.

00:12:03.089 --> 00:12:05.758
Chaos Magnalia!

00:12:05.858 --> 00:12:06.659
Buddy!

00:12:06.759 --> 00:12:08.894
You really gotta wake up.

