I just wanna sleep just a little while longer.

00:12:29.849 --> 00:12:30.916
DAN: Drago!

00:12:31.016 --> 00:12:32.118
Drago!

00:12:32.218 --> 00:12:34.186
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Please, just a few more minutes.

00:12:34.286 --> 00:12:35.454
DAN: Drago! DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Huh?

00:12:35.554 --> 00:12:36.622
Wait a minute.

00:12:36.722 --> 00:12:37.823
That's Dan!

00:12:37.923 --> 00:12:39.825
[battle music]

00:12:40.759 --> 00:12:42.528
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Blitz Hammer!

00:12:42.628 --> 00:12:43.929
Ha!

00:12:44.029 --> 00:12:44.964
What?

00:12:45.064 --> 00:12:46.298
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): That's impossible.

00:12:46.398 --> 00:12:47.466
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): [growls]

00:12:47.566 --> 00:12:48.901
Believe it suckers.

00:12:49.001 --> 00:12:49.969
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Dan.

00:12:50.069 --> 00:12:52.371
You had me scared for a minute.

00:12:52.471 --> 00:12:55.074
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Sorry, but I'm back now, thanks to you.

00:12:55.174 --> 00:12:57.476
Ability activate!

00:12:57.576 --> 00:13:00.346
Blitz Superior!

00:13:00.446 --> 00:13:02.281
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): Stubborn children.

00:13:02.381 --> 00:13:04.783
Tempest Shield!

00:13:04.884 --> 00:13:08.754
[groans]

00:13:08.854 --> 00:13:13.759
[growls]

00:13:13.859 --> 00:13:14.760
Yeah!

00:13:14.860 --> 00:13:16.729
You will never take me.

00:13:16.829 --> 00:13:18.030
I just did, creep.

00:13:18.130 --> 00:13:21.367
Bakugan brawl.

00:13:21.467 --> 00:13:22.301
Bakugan scan.

00:13:22.401 --> 00:13:25.004
[roaring]

00:13:25.905 --> 00:13:29.041
BARODIUS: Thunder Gladiator!

00:13:29.141 --> 00:13:31.710
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): Photon Gladiator!

00:13:31.810 --> 00:13:33.879
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Blitz Reflector!

00:13:33.979 --> 00:13:36.282
[explosion]

00:13:36.382 --> 00:13:38.184
[growls]

00:13:38.284 --> 00:13:40.119
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Spire Dragon!

00:13:40.219 --> 00:13:42.021
[growls]

00:13:42.121 --> 00:13:44.423
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): [moans in pain]

00:13:44.523 --> 00:13:47.526
You are one tough cookie, Drago.

00:13:47.626 --> 00:13:48.827
Fools!

00:13:48.928 --> 00:13:51.797
It's a little too soon to be congratulating yourselves.

00:13:51.897 --> 00:13:53.299
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): Hyper Guns End!

00:13:53.399 --> 00:13:55.134
[roars]

00:13:55.234 --> 00:13:56.535
Let's go!

00:13:56.635 --> 00:13:59.305
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Blitz Superior!

00:13:59.405 --> 00:14:02.741
[crackling sounds]

00:14:02.841 --> 00:14:04.677
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): [grunts]

00:14:04.777 --> 00:14:08.113
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): [groans]

00:14:08.214 --> 00:14:11.083
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): [screams]

00:14:11.183 --> 00:14:13.118
Dharak!

00:14:13.219 --> 00:14:14.119
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): Drago!

00:14:17.590 --> 00:14:19.058
CODE EVE (VOICEOVER): Battle over.

00:14:23.829 --> 00:14:25.164
Whoa.

00:14:25.264 --> 00:14:26.899
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): We did it.

00:14:26.999 --> 00:14:29.101
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): I can't believe I lost.

00:14:29.201 --> 00:14:32.304
This is an outrage.

00:14:32.404 --> 00:14:33.339
NURZAK: My, my.

00:14:33.439 --> 00:14:36.375
How the mighty have fallen, Baronius.

00:14:36.475 --> 00:14:41.880
[growls] [grunts] Get back you insolent fools.

00:14:41.981 --> 00:14:45.017
You cannot keep the power of the Sacred Orb from me.

00:14:45.117 --> 00:14:47.753
Bakugan brawl!

00:14:47.853 --> 00:14:50.356
Bakugan scan!

00:14:50.456 --> 00:14:52.791
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): [roars]

00:14:52.891 --> 00:14:55.794
Castle Knights, fall back and protect Queen Serena.

00:14:55.894 --> 00:14:57.863
NURZAK: Have you no shame, Barodius?

00:14:57.963 --> 00:15:01.333
Can you not accept defeat in a dignified fashion?

00:15:01.433 --> 00:15:02.568
Be quiet.

00:15:02.668 --> 00:15:06.538
Dharak, it is time we take what is ours.

00:15:06.639 --> 00:15:08.274
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): I couldn't agree more.

00:15:08.374 --> 00:15:09.575
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Dan?

00:15:09.675 --> 00:15:10.709
I'm with you.

00:15:10.809 --> 00:15:13.712
Bakugan brawl!

00:15:13.812 --> 00:15:15.147
Bakugan scan.

00:15:20.119 --> 00:15:21.487
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): [growls]

00:15:21.587 --> 00:15:25.457
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): [roars]

00:15:25.557 --> 00:15:26.959
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): Yes.

00:15:27.059 --> 00:15:31.597
I can feel it's mighty power filling me up inside.

00:15:31.697 --> 00:15:33.565
It's like Code Eve said, Dan.

00:15:33.666 --> 00:15:35.567
You can't fight destiny.

00:15:35.668 --> 00:15:37.503
[evil laugh]

00:15:37.603 --> 00:15:38.470
Grr.

00:15:38.570 --> 00:15:41.907
[maniacal laugh] Huh?

00:15:42.007 --> 00:15:43.475
What's happening?

00:15:43.575 --> 00:15:46.378
DHARAK (VOICEOVER): The power, it won't stop.

00:15:46.478 --> 00:15:48.047
It just keeps coming.

00:15:48.147 --> 00:15:52.117
I don't know if I can take any more!

00:15:52.217 --> 00:16:00.492
[screaming]

00:16:00.592 --> 00:16:01.493
DAN: Drago!

00:16:01.593 --> 00:16:02.494
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): Dan!

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:10.202
CODE EVE (VOICEOVER): Congratulations, gentlemen.

00:16:10.302 --> 00:16:11.970
You were victorious in your battle

00:16:12.071 --> 00:16:13.572
against Barodius and Dharak.

00:16:13.672 --> 00:16:16.775
Now, as promised, I would bestow my powers onto you.

00:16:16.875 --> 00:16:17.676
Use them wisely.

00:16:17.776 --> 00:16:19.411
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): [roars]

00:16:19.511 --> 00:16:22.014
CODE EVE (VOICEOVER): May I present, Titanium Dragonoid.

00:16:22.114 --> 00:16:30.889
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): [moans] [groans] [roars]

00:16:30.989 --> 00:16:32.458
You just evolved again!

00:16:32.558 --> 00:16:33.359
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): I know.

00:16:33.459 --> 00:16:34.793
I feel incredible.

00:16:34.893 --> 00:16:38.564
CODE EVE (VOICEOVER): Now you rule the entire Bakugan race.

00:16:38.664 --> 00:16:40.833
Wow, that's some responsibility.

00:16:40.933 --> 00:16:42.534
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): I never entered into this war

00:16:42.634 --> 00:16:44.803
to become a ruler.

00:16:44.903 --> 00:16:47.439
Neither did I. The Brawlers have only ever wanted peace

00:16:47.539 --> 00:16:48.841
for our friends the Bakugan.

00:16:48.941 --> 00:16:51.276
We don't need to rule them, you see.

00:16:51.377 --> 00:16:54.046
We just wanna live in harmony beside them, just

00:16:54.146 --> 00:16:56.682
as all good friends should.

00:16:56.782 --> 00:16:58.083
CODE EVE (VOICEOVER): I understand.

00:16:58.183 --> 00:17:02.221
Your decision is a noble one and I respect it greatly.

00:17:05.357 --> 00:17:08.060
[energy beam]

00:17:08.160 --> 00:17:11.497
It's so hard to believe that the war is finally over

00:17:11.597 --> 00:17:14.566
and that peace has once again returned to our homeland,

00:17:14.666 --> 00:17:17.903
but with so much devastation it will be a while before things

00:17:18.003 --> 00:17:19.304
are back to normal.

00:17:19.405 --> 00:17:22.274
Nah, I bet things will get back on track.

00:17:22.374 --> 00:17:25.144
You're right, Dan.

00:17:25.244 --> 00:17:27.880
It makes me hopeful seeing everyone so happy again.

00:17:33.185 --> 00:17:35.421
Does this mean you're leaving?

00:17:35.521 --> 00:17:38.624
Well, we did finish what we came to do.

00:17:38.724 --> 00:17:41.260
Then I guess this is farewell.

00:17:41.360 --> 00:17:42.327
I guess.

00:17:42.428 --> 00:17:45.164
[gentle music playing]

00:17:46.532 --> 00:17:47.733
DAN: Be cool, Ren.

00:17:47.833 --> 00:17:48.634
REN: I will.

00:17:48.734 --> 00:17:50.536
Take care of yourself, friend.

00:17:50.636 --> 00:17:53.005
Thanks again for everything.

00:17:53.105 --> 00:17:56.041
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): I'm sure we'll meet again, Linehalt.

00:17:56.141 --> 00:17:58.510
Now that the royal family and its supporters

00:17:58.610 --> 00:18:00.979
have been defeated, I shall return to Gundalia

00:18:01.080 --> 00:18:05.284
to form a new government, one that

00:18:05.384 --> 00:18:07.085
will only have friendly relations

00:18:07.186 --> 00:18:08.587
with its neighboring planet.

00:18:08.687 --> 00:18:11.457
That is, if you will permit it, Queen Serena.

00:18:11.557 --> 00:18:13.258
Of course.

00:18:13.358 --> 00:18:15.861
I think this war has taught us all a valuable lesson

00:18:15.961 --> 00:18:18.597
about the importance of peace.

00:18:18.697 --> 00:18:21.300
LINEHALT (VOICEOVER): Ren, now that I'm a Castle Knight, I

00:18:21.400 --> 00:18:23.402
would like to remain here on Neathia

00:18:23.502 --> 00:18:26.405
so that I may continue to serve.

00:18:26.505 --> 00:18:29.007
I promise I'll take good care of him.

00:18:29.108 --> 00:18:30.776
OK.

00:18:30.876 --> 00:18:34.146
Marucho, I'll never forget you my friend.

00:18:34.246 --> 00:18:37.616
I won't forget you either, buddy.

00:18:37.716 --> 00:18:38.684
Take care.

00:18:38.784 --> 00:18:39.685
You too.

00:18:43.088 --> 00:18:46.225
And so, I bid you all adieu, Battle Brawlers.

00:18:46.325 --> 00:18:51.997
[transport beams]

00:18:52.097 --> 00:18:53.899
[ships blast]

00:18:53.999 --> 00:18:57.769
Well, I guess that's our cue then, Akwimos.

00:18:57.870 --> 00:18:59.671
AKWIMOS (VOICEOVER): Yeah, sure looks like it.

00:18:59.771 --> 00:19:00.906
I, uh--

00:19:01.006 --> 00:19:02.341
AKWIMOS (VOICEOVER): I'm going to miss you.

00:19:02.441 --> 00:19:05.611
You're the peanut butter to my jelly.

00:19:05.711 --> 00:19:08.647
Cool as the rule, dude.

00:19:08.747 --> 00:19:11.183
It was an honor to battle alongside a fine warrior

00:19:11.283 --> 00:19:12.451
like you, Hawktor.

00:19:12.551 --> 00:19:14.219
HAWKTOR (VOICEOVER): I learned a great deal in my time

00:19:14.319 --> 00:19:15.120
with you, Shun.

00:19:15.220 --> 00:19:16.922
Thank you for everything.

00:19:17.022 --> 00:19:19.625
I promised myself I wasn't gonna do this!

00:19:19.725 --> 00:19:23.028
Oh man, I'm really gonna miss you, dude.

00:19:23.128 --> 00:19:25.097
A guy never forgets his first Bakugan.

00:19:25.197 --> 00:19:27.366
Just promise me you won't forget me either because that

00:19:27.466 --> 00:19:28.834
would bust me up inside.

00:19:28.934 --> 00:19:30.569
[sobs]

00:19:30.669 --> 00:19:31.870
COREDEM (VOICE OVER): OK, take it easy.

00:19:31.970 --> 00:19:33.238
I promise.

00:19:33.338 --> 00:19:35.240
You're a solid dude, Jake.

00:19:35.340 --> 00:19:37.543
Take care of yourself.

00:19:37.643 --> 00:19:39.845
ARANAUT (VOICEOVER): Shall I send them off, princess?

00:19:39.945 --> 00:19:41.880
Yes, I'd appreciate that Aranaut.

00:19:48.654 --> 00:19:51.390
Dan, thanks to you and the Brawlers

00:19:51.490 --> 00:19:53.492
we have peace once again.

00:19:53.592 --> 00:19:57.462
Thank you for everything you've done for us.

00:19:57.563 --> 00:19:59.631
We are forever in your debt.

00:19:59.731 --> 00:20:01.133
No sweat, guys.

00:20:01.233 --> 00:20:04.136
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): That's what friends are for.

00:20:04.236 --> 00:20:08.407
[transport beams]

00:20:08.507 --> 00:20:10.609
I really miss Dan and the others.

00:20:10.709 --> 00:20:11.910
I wonder how they're doing.

00:20:12.010 --> 00:20:13.579
Yeah, oh, I know.

00:20:13.679 --> 00:20:14.680
I hope they're OK.

00:20:14.780 --> 00:20:17.549
He hasn't even called his own mother, huh.

00:20:17.649 --> 00:20:20.586
But I guess I should be used to that.

00:20:20.686 --> 00:20:21.787
Oh, my goodness.

00:20:21.887 --> 00:20:23.021
Where has the day gone?

00:20:23.121 --> 00:20:25.090
I have to get home and fix dinner.

00:20:25.190 --> 00:20:27.459
See you later, hon.

00:20:27.559 --> 00:20:29.561
Bye Mrs. Kuso.

00:20:29.661 --> 00:20:32.364
I wonder what I should make.

00:20:32.464 --> 00:20:33.632
DAN: Hey, mom!

00:20:33.732 --> 00:20:35.300
Huh?

00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:38.236
We're back!

00:20:38.337 --> 00:20:40.205
Daniel?

00:20:40.305 --> 00:20:41.106
Oh!

00:20:41.206 --> 00:20:44.109
[giggles] Hey, guys!

00:20:44.209 --> 00:20:46.578
[laughs]

00:20:46.678 --> 00:20:51.583
[laughs]

00:20:51.683 --> 00:20:53.819
[laughs]

00:20:53.919 --> 00:20:55.354
MARUCHO: Did you miss us?

00:20:55.454 --> 00:20:57.422
Mom, I'm home!

00:20:57.522 --> 00:21:00.993
Of course we did, but only a little.

00:21:01.093 --> 00:21:02.394
Ha!

00:21:02.494 --> 00:21:04.296
[laughs]

00:21:04.396 --> 00:21:08.066
[battle music]

00:21:08.166 --> 00:21:09.968
ANNOUNCER: Good evening, ladies and gentlemen,

00:21:10.068 --> 00:21:13.305
the Bakugan battle between Dan Kuso and Koji Beetle

00:21:13.405 --> 00:21:14.773
will now commence.

00:21:14.873 --> 00:21:18.010
So you're the famous Dan Kuso, huh.

00:21:18.110 --> 00:21:20.312
I've always wanted to fight you, pal.

00:21:20.412 --> 00:21:23.482
Actually, we already have, buddy.

00:21:23.582 --> 00:21:25.384
DRAGO (VOICEOVER): He's not going to remember that.

00:21:25.484 --> 00:21:26.284
Huh?

00:21:26.385 --> 00:21:27.486
What did you say?

00:21:27.586 --> 00:21:29.688
I was just saying, good luck!

00:21:29.788 --> 00:21:33.358
ANNOUNCER: Bakugan Field, open!

00:21:33.458 --> 00:21:37.329
[grunts] Bakugan brawl!

00:21:37.429 --> 00:21:41.667
[theme music]